1) Adding a new employer

Precondition:
Log in by any valid user (E.g.: Student, Pass: 909090)


Steps to reproduce:
1. From the Menu left choose "Словари", then click "Сотрудники"
2. In the opening list of registered employers click on "PLUS" sign in the right top corner
3. Add Worker's name, surname, middle name and phone number
4. Click "Создать" button


Expected result:

A new employer is added to the list




2) Editing details of counter parties

Precondition:
Log in by any valid user (E.g.: Student, Pass: 909090)


Steps to reproduce:
1. From the Menu left choose "Словари", then click "Стороны сделок"
2. Tap on any of counter parties from the opening list
3. Edit any of Pro cust name, Pro cust address or Pro cust phone
4. Click "Сохранить" button


Expected result:

The details of counter parts are successfully edited


3) Changing user's Email address

Precondition:
Log in by any valid user (E.g.: Student, Pass: 909090)


Steps to reproduce:
1. Click the user's icon in the right top corner, then click "Профиль"
2. Make any changes in "Адрес email" field
3. Click "Сохранить" button


Expected result:

The Email address is successfully edited and saved


